and my husband is busy too.

550
00:47:07,041 --> 00:47:09,691
Please take care of Kew and Kram for a while.

551
00:47:09,966 --> 00:47:10,866
I'll pick them up in the evening.

552
00:47:11,191 --> 00:47:11,666
No problem.

553
00:47:12,266 --> 00:47:13,591
I'll go now then.

554
00:47:13,791 --> 00:47:15,691
Be good, Kew and Kram.

555
00:47:15,766 --> 00:47:16,866
-No problem.
-No problem.

556
00:47:16,991 --> 00:47:18,366
Okay.

557
00:47:18,766 --> 00:47:22,641
Brother Ram, I'll go now.

558
00:47:24,866 --> 00:47:25,991
Mother is leaving, kids.

559
00:47:29,566 --> 00:47:30,166
Come in.

560
00:47:34,016 --> 00:47:36,266
Wow, tattoo.

561
00:47:37,116 --> 00:47:38,966
Cool.

562
00:47:39,391 --> 00:47:48,141
-Let us see it.
-Let us see it.

563
00:47:48,141 --> 00:47:50,341
Children, there's chocolate.

564
00:47:50,341 --> 00:47:51,766
It's in the usual place. Go get it.

565
00:47:51,766 --> 00:47:52,591
Over there.

566
00:47:52,791 --> 00:47:54,391
-Yay!
-Yay!

567
00:48:02,916 --> 00:48:04,941
Are you afraid of children?

568
00:48:07,208 --> 00:48:08,343
Oh, my!

569
00:48:08,352 --> 00:48:13,466
Ram, who isn't afraid of anything,
is afraid of children.

570
00:48:17,841 --> 00:48:19,191
Because I don't get along with children.

571
00:48:20,341 --> 00:48:21,691
They're completely different from the dogs.

572
00:48:21,691 --> 00:48:23,066
Oh.

573
00:48:23,991 --> 00:48:26,316
Wow, dogs.
